lly intersected. The volume includes a complete bibliography of her publications.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aJewsxCivilizationyTo 70 A.D. 0aJewsxHistoryy168 B.C.-135 A.D. 0aJewszRomexCivilization. 4aIsrael (Altertum) /Alte Geschichte. 4aIsrael (Altertum) /Religion. 4aPapyrus. 4aRömisches Reich /Religion. 7aRELIGION / Judaism / History.2bisacsh  aJewish law.  aProvincial Jurisdiction.  aconflicts of law.  alegal contracts.1 aPogorelsky, Ofer, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishz978311099454408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022z9783110994537oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831107706050 cprintz978311019144840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311077043840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110770438423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110770438/original  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099454-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022